&lt;p>Teaching philosophy is one thing living is another.&lt;/p>
&lt;p>“Karmanye Vadhikaraste”. &lt;br>
Means you have control over karma, your process. &lt;br>
So guide and control the process.&lt;/p>
&lt;p>“Adhikaraste MaFaleshu Kadachna”. &lt;br>
Doesn’t mean without expecting a result. &lt;br>
Nor does it mean result for someone else &lt;br>
or work for society or higher cause etc.&lt;/p></description></item></channel></rss>